图挂了，关于第二个问题，下面写个Shapeless的做示范，如果你还想要更多的功能，请自行补充。

    /**
     * Add a shapeless recipe that crafts a enchanted book
     *
     * @param enchantment The enchantment fo the enchanted book
     * @param level       the level of the enchantment
     * @param items       a list of items that make up the recipe(Available type: {[url=home.php?mod=space&uid=41191]@link[/url] net.minecraft.item.ItemStack}, {@link net.minecraft.item.Item}, and {@link net.minecraft.block.Block})
     */
    public static void addEnchantedBookShapelessRecipe(Enchantment enchantment, int level, Object... items) {
        ItemStack enchantedBook = new ItemStack(Items.enchanted_book);
        enchantedBook.addEnchantment(enchantment, level);
        GameRegistry.addShapelessRecipe(enchantedBook, items);
    }复制代码

